      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780769815476,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1) look up all participants for a given chat \n        - chatId is partionKey\n        - participantId is the sortKey\n        - A Query on the chatId partition key will return all participants for a given chat.\n\n2) look up all chats for a given user.\n        - GSI\n            - participantId is the PrimaryKey\n            - chatId is the sortKey\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1) look up all participants for a given chat \n        - chatId is partionKey\n        - participantId is the sortKey\n        - A Query on the chatId partition key will return all participants for a given chat.\n\n2) look up all chats for a given user.\n        - GSI\n            - participantId is the PrimaryKey\n            - chatId is the sortKey\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
